videos.headline: Colorado's Shenault escapes tackles for 42-yard TD
videos.description: Laviska Shenault doesn't let the Air Force defense take him down as he breaks tackles and rushes to the end zone for a 42-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Colorado's Shenault escapes tackles for 42-yard TD) 2019/9/14

videos.headline: Waters wins 81-yard race for Air Force TD
videos.description: Benjamin Waters hauls in a nice pass from Air Force QB Donald Hammond III, escapes a tackle and takes off all on his own for an 81-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Waters wins 81-yard race for Air Force TD) 2019/9/14

videos.headline: Shenault forces OT with late Colorado TD
videos.description: Laviska Shenault Jr. runs through the pile for a 2-yard touchdown to tie Air Force at 23-23 in the final seconds of the 4th quarter forcing overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shenault forces OT with late Colorado TD) 2019/9/14
